This is documentation of all the different ways the blog controller will be used and the URIs I have designed for them

1. A single blog will be accessed through it's id.

GET api/blogs/{blogId}

2. All the blogs of an user will be accessed through the users corresponding ID

GET api/blogs?userId=123

3. Blogs will be posted by users

POST api/blogs

Request body :

{
  title : "title goes here",
  body : "the main content of the blog goes here"
}

4. An user can update their blog

PUT api/blogs/{blogId}

Request body :

{
  title : "title goes here",
  body : "the main content of the blog goes here"
}

5. An user can delete their blog

DELETE api/blogs/{blogId}
